description:
*Overcoming Addictions: Victory Over Sin* | Honestly, most of us struggle with some form of addiction. In today's LED Live episode, we invite Chad and Fadia Kreuzer of _Anchor Point Films_ to help us address the actions we can take to overcome all types of addictions. If we are honest, most of us struggle with one form of addiction and this is a practical, life-changing presentation that we can all benefit from.
